               <p>Cross- examined. Q. How do you know them? A. By this mark of sixpence on them - it is a common price, but this is my writing - we had but these six on the counter and missed them.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. They were not marked when they were taken from me.</p>
               <p>HUGH CASH. They are exactly in the same state as when I found them in her bag.</p>
